{"tid":1514973,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"陳雲：香港議員的行為，在美國人面前丟人現眼","createTime":"2019-08-29T03:11:39.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-29T04:22:36.000Z","uid":97944,"like":16,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"8b8278295927c0b48845bfb07566d6ad56a2201d","tid":1514973,"uid":97944,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T03:11:39.000Z","msg":"美國的流行網報《野獸日報》報導香港議員代表團在美國與部分美國議員會談的內情。是次會面是秘密會議。該報得到兩位熟悉內情的人提供消息：香港的議員不同意《香港人權及民主法案》，有些更是全然反對。<br />\n<br />\n《野獸日報》是流行報紙，有自己意見，但並無黨派立場。<br />\n<br />\n陳雲認為，在影響全港命運的事情上，香港議員不應該參與外國議員的閉門會議，只能參與公開演說的國會聽證會或公開陳情的會談。閉門會議是不道德的交易，也對不住香港選民。泛民議員參加了密談，之後委託葉劉淑儀開記者會，泛民缺席，已經說明一切。<br />\n<br />\n密談有君子協定，雙方不能公開內容，但葉劉淑儀回港開記者會，泛民議員又反對葉劉淑儀的講法，各執一詞。美方議員見到這種醜態出現，即刻通知美國報紙爆料，招呼這群破壞密約的香港議員：原來香港議員反對《香港人權及民主法案》，有些更是全然反對。<br />\n<br />\n香港議員的行為，在美國人面前丟人現眼，可謂醜怪到難以形容。但他們是香港人選出來的。<br />\n<br />\n報紙是如實報導。因為美國很多議員不認識香港，故此是次秘密會談對香港傷害極大。<br />\n<br />\n//During a secret meeting in Montana last week, people from both sides of the political rift involving China discussed legislation in Congress aimed at Beijing.<br />\n&hellip;In Montana, Hong Kong officials disagreed on the bill, with some advocating against it all together, according to two individuals familiar with the conversation.//<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.thedailybeast.com/hong-kong-officials-met-with-us-lawmakers-about-punishing-china/?via=FB_Page&amp;source=TDB&amp;fbclid=IwAR3rjRapjsm1xCUlgq5MrCrLoTZ5pytaH3jnLeLCApG4E3S4zJbkV3aNUqk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thedailybeast.com%2Fhong-kong-officials-met-with-us-lawmakers-about-punishing-china%2F%3Fvia%3DFB_Page%26source%3DTDB%26fbclid%3DIwAR3rjRapjsm1xCUlgq5MrCrLoTZ5pytaH3jnLeLCApG4E3S4zJbkV3aNUqk&d=BKn7HUA2FwSq4MnMa2nFTGLZ6li1RkmcNQmTobTGNbY%3D&h=9b2d28ff\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.thedailybeast.com/hong-kong-officials-met-with-us-lawmakers-about-punishing-china/?via=FB_Page&amp;source=TDB&amp;fbclid=IwAR3rjRapjsm1xCUlgq5MrCrLoTZ5pytaH3jnLeLCApG4E3S4zJbkV3aNUqk</a>"},{"pid":"d2aac4ce1e56d866e56daa7f5d89b2fa0546c8ed","tid":1514973,"uid":35842,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T03:12:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/OTykUks.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FOTykUks.jpg&h=e262c427&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3J6Zqr9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3J6Zqr9.jpg&h=398279dd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n唔好意思借個post宣傳一下<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/wjFi3Tp.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FwjFi3Tp.jpg&h=1a5d1359&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">901 和你塞 13:00 見</span></span> <a href=\"http://t.me/stuckwithyou\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithyou&d=BKn7HUA2FwSq4MnMa2nFTGLZ6li1RkmcNQmTobTGNbY%3D&h=78545ee3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">t.me/stuckwithyou</a><br />\n<br />\n現有文宣集合 (Google Drive)<br />\n<a href=\"https://drive.google.com/open?id=128hRA8sm5aa2jUlNJAzPtGkYt2_3n-z2\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdrive.google.com%2Fopen%3Fid%3D128hRA8sm5aa2jUlNJAzPtGkYt2_3n-z2&d=BKn7HUA2FwSq4MnMa2nFTGLZ6li1RkmcNQmTobTGNbY%3D&h=d305a8d7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://drive.google.com/open?id=128hRA8sm5aa2jUlNJAzPtGkYt2_3n-z2</a><br />\n請隨便使用，用自己的方法幫忙發送文宣出去，感謝<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/LoOsXdt.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FLoOsXdt.jpg&h=b1104862&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: gold;\">每晚10點</span></strong></span>大家開大嗰窗嗌口號<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n當係抒發下或者互相鼓勵都好<br />\n<br />\n真係有人嗌㗎 唔洗怕醜<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/fit.tsoi/videos/18959603870986